API Server Setup
----------------
npm init
npm i express --save
npm i @babel/core @babel/node @babel/preset-env --save-dev
code .babelrc
add this to that file
{
  "presets": [
    "@babel/preset-env"
  ]
}
npm i nodemon --save-dev
edit package.json and add the following to scripts:
"start": "nodemon --exec babel-node ./server.js"
npm i dotenv --save